{"tid":1455082,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"機場困獸鬥 目標達成 走啊！ 附交通update","createTime":"2019-08-12T08:39:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T08:43:14.000Z","uid":123713,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"717e786ea81ed5a40513d4aea7afbc44e56c4df1","tid":1455082,"uid":123713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T08:39:20.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">癱瘓機場目標已達成</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">1.成個機場都係狗同防暴<br />\n2.機管局被逼停飛所有航班<br />\n3.好可能旅客清晒就會封場<br />\n4.仲要機場冇路走 一封出東涌條橋就收皮！<br />\n5.今日入得機場既 全部都係追post追得最貼既深黃 唔好犧牲啊！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n全身以退 不被捕！<br />\n留得青山在啊！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nT1有咩事記住去T2<br />\n<br />\n*去T2方法*:<br />\n- 係離境嗰層，行去機鐵個位，有escalator落一層就係T2<br />\n- 去到T2上一層有好多餐廳、food court，有戲院！<br />\n- 去到T2，如落一層就係停車場<br />\n<br />\n*去富豪酒店 Regal Airport Hotel方法*:<br />\n- Arrival Hall A 有條行人天橋，只有一條路，行過去就係<br />\n- 現時只有Regal正門可以合法上的士、Uber (不過今日唔知啲車入唔入到)<br />\n<br />\n*去國泰城方法* :<br />\n- Arrival Hall 任何一條樓梯落去 (有防煙門嗰啲) 就到巴士站嗰層，有幾個shuttle係去CXCity and KA House/ 民航處"},{"pid":"281376814692e8178a79a624ba1832f0c91aeda8","tid":1455082,"uid":123713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T08:39:27.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">癱瘓機場目標已達成</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">1.成個機場都係狗同防暴<br />\n2.機管局被逼停飛所有航班<br />\n3.好可能旅客清晒就會封場<br />\n4.仲要機場冇路走 一封出東涌條橋就收皮！<br />\n5.今日入得機場既 全部都係追post追得最貼既深黃 唔好犧牲啊！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n全身以退 不被捕！<br />\n留得青山在啊！</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"17bc42d8f89a59e883300233066b9e30022a7c8f","tid":1455082,"uid":160383,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T08:40:30.000Z","msg":"無旅客既機場 只係一個孤島<br />\n唔需要死守 唔需要佔據<br />\n<br />\n黑警點解會唔敢開火？ 無哂人仲唔開火？<br />\n機場幾時變左聖地？<br />\n有光環既係旅客，唔係機場<br />\n<br />\n黑警鎖機場 洗開火咩？<br />\n係個門口一個一個登記 已經玩完<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n叫人留既 唔係鬼 就係戇鳩仔<br />\n屌哂你地老母全家"},{"pid":"113b3bd9f2950fa9dbdb9a6c42cf61d4d767f26d","tid":1455082,"uid":165246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T08:41:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">達到經濟問題啦 走呀！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">今日所有航班已取消!<br />\n機場圍捕無路走！<br />\n所有手足請即散<br />\n記得係一齊散<br />\n唔好落單！<br />\n擇日再戰<br />\n切實執行不被捕原則！<br />\n仲有咩好留呀 叫你留個d 自己諗下係咪鬼啦<br />\n仲有咩好留呀<br />\n仲有咩好留先<br />\n點解仲要留係到</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ngYyt3j.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FngYyt3j.png&h=916dd304&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GSMoRgG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGSMoRgG.png&h=734c1f44&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UYUBrP8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUYUBrP8.png&h=f9aef586&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"070eaea63e2071581fe21484717b64934c4d001a","tid":1455082,"uid":123713,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T08:43:04.000Z","msg":"重點重點！聽住。前地勤教路，如果有需要請打火警鐘，機場設計火警鐘一響，所有門都會開哂"},{"pid":"8e2862b413f77bca3e270273c8e17ec7582d70ff","tid":1455082,"uid":123713,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T08:43:14.000Z","msg":"重點重點！聽住。前地勤教路，如果有需要請打火警鐘，機場設計火警鐘一響，所有門都會開哂"}]}